title: Is “Baron Trump’s Marvelous Underground Journey” a Real Book from the 1890s?
subtitle: Two books from the 1890s contain seemingly eerie connections to modern-day politics.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Author Ingersoll Lockwood wrote the books "Baron Trump's Marvelous Underground Journey" and "1900: or, The Last President"  in the 1890s.
